embeddings.title: Tagline & Intro
embeddings.text: Trusted IT. Smarter AI. Lasting Impact. Resonira Technologies empowers businesses with future-ready digital solutions that echo innovation, precision, and impact. We specialize in scalable, secure, and innovative technology solutions that drive growth and transform industries.

embeddings.title: Company Stats
embeddings.text: Stats & Highlights: 25+ Projects Delivered; 20+ Happy Clients; 3+ Years Experience; 98% Client Satisfaction.

embeddings.title: Testimonials
embeddings.text: Testimonials: Sarah Chen (CEO, TechFlow Solutions): Resonira's AI-powered recommendation engine increased conversion rates by 40%. Michael Rodriguez (CTO, Blockchain Ventures): Robust and secure smart contract platform; launched ahead of schedule. Dr. Priya Sharma (Founder, MedTech Innovations): AI diagnostic system reduced analysis time by 60%.

embeddings.title: Process
embeddings.text: Delivery Process: 01 Discovery & Planning – requirements and detailed plan. 02 Design & Architecture – solution architecture and UX. 03 Development & Testing – agile build and QA. 04 Deployment & Support – launch and ongoing maintenance.

embeddings.title: Technologies
embeddings.text: Technologies: Frontend – React, TypeScript, Vue.js; Backend – Node.js; AI/ML – Python, TensorFlow; Cloud – AWS; DevOps – Docker, Kubernetes; Database – MongoDB, Redis; API – GraphQL.

embeddings.title: Mission & Vision
embeddings.text: Mission: To resonate innovation into every industry by building reliable, scalable, and futuristic technology solutions. Vision: To be a global leader in crafting technology that echoes excellence and empowers businesses worldwide.

embeddings.title: Values
embeddings.text: Innovation that Inspires; Integrity in Action; Collaboration that Resonates; Excellence in Delivery.

embeddings.title: Services
embeddings.text: We provide AI solutions, software development, and related technology services, including AI/ML systems and automation, custom web & mobile apps, cloud & infrastructure, and digital transformation consulting.
